      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·陳風·006.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">墓門.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>墓門有梅，有鴞萃止。夫也不良，歌以誶之。訊予不顧，顛倒思予。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>At the gate to the tombs there are plum trees,
And there are owls collecting on them.
That man is not good,
And I sing this song to admonish him.
I admonish him, but he will not regard me; —
When he is overthrown, he will think of me.</seg>
      </tuv>
